name: Go to the Store and Buy 400 Gallons of Milk
name_original: Go to the Store and Buy 400 Gallons of Milk
description:
Go to the Store and Buy 400 Gallons of Milk is a platformer game developed by Cucklord. It was originally released in 2021.
Go to the Store and Buy 400 Gallons of Milk is available on Web. The game is sold via itch.io.
